commit.message: Debian Package Updates
Updated to version 0.9.3
Added note for skipping version 0.9.2 to 0.9.3
Fixed unbound variable in WGET_TEST_STRING
Fix typo
Updated Version strings for release
Updated to include new MEDIA:CONTENT tag description
Removed Tested on BSD Versions as we moved on
Updated to include MEDIA CONTENT tag description
Updated comments sed statements for finding URLs
Filter MEDIA:CONTENT tags for video or audio files
Fix error in sed statement, order of characters
Fix "unset" with "unset -v" as required
Improved RSS blank title handling.
Added support for <media:content> tags
Formatting fix.
Added more "unset -v i" after for loops to prevent possible issues
Small potential bug fix and updated changelog.
Fixed WGET loop error (i instead of INTERVAL)
Updated manual to explain new Wget Default User-Agent
Added option to restore default WGET User Agent per feed
Improved parsing of WGET Options
Added issues reported by xrogaan on github and status fixed.
Added SURPLUSINDEX to hold items for marking as downloaded.
Use TITLES instead of FILENAMES when possible marking downloaded
Fixes to removing zero size downloaded files.
